Class Doctor

java.lang.Object
org.CSPT.sc2001_grp1_proj1.entity.Users
org.CSPT.sc2001_grp1_proj1.entity.HospitalStaff
org.CSPT.sc2001_grp1_proj1.FunctionRoles.Doctor
public class Doctor extends HospitalStaff
Represents the Doctor role in the hospital management system. Provides functionality for managing patient medical records, scheduling and managing appointments, and recording appointment outcomes.
